        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Empowering Law Enforcement for Safer Firearm Transfers Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill modifies procedural requirements related to the transfer of machine guns, destructive devices, and certain other firearms.</p> <p>Specifically, the bill requires the chief law enforcement officer of the jurisdiction in which the transferee primarily resides to be notified of the pending transfer and given 90 days to object.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
